The Lunar Isle Mine (also called the Lunar Mine) is located in the north-eastern part of Lunar Isle. It contains a rune essence rock in the centre. It also contains the only known place to mine Lunar ore, in addition to gem rocks just like in Shilo Village. Cyrisus can be found wounded in a nearby cave accessible through a crack, starting the Dream Mentor quest.

The entrance to the mine.

Contents

  • 1 Rocks
  • 2 Monsters
  • 3 Personalities
  • 4 Music

Rocks[edit | edit source]

  • In the centre is rune essence.
  • To the west are six gold rocks, and stalagmites which can be mined for Lunar ore.
  • To the south are three silver rocks.
  • To the south-east are three gem rocks.
  • To the north-east is one gold, two silver and a gem rock.

Cyrisus can be found before and during the Dream Mentor quest.
